   <pb facs="23"/>
   <head>An Aduertisement.</head>
   <p>COurteous Reader; I shall entreat you where you finde some few, either <gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap>iterall, or verball faults, to haue recourse to this follow<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ing <hi>Errata</hi> committed by the Printer, which will bee verie vnpleasing to the Reuerend Authour (who is many miles distant from the Presse) which errors if you shall vouchsafe to pardon in this Impression, they shall be more carefully a<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>mended in the next.</p>
   <closer>
      <signed>N. B.</signed>
   </closer>
